Summary: Picture taken of the moon on 12/12. Perhaps a photo anomaly.
divs: sighting detailsi was taking a picture of the moon and this showed up in the photo. it may be nothing more than water. i don't know. the fact that the light seemed concentrated on one side (that facing the moon\light source) seemed unusual to me though it would make sense were it simply a drop of water. i cropped the picture because it was huge and emailed the interesting part to a friend who ran it through some enhancements and this is what turned out. i'll include the original and the enhancements. i'm fairly certain it's simply an anomaly but i figured i'd submit it regardless. hope i'm not wasting anyone's time.
